sorcer.core.invoker

Class AltInvoker<V>

  • java.lang.Object
    • sorcer.core.invoker.Observable
      • sorcer.core.invoker.ServiceInvoker<V>
        • sorcer.core.invoker.AltInvoker<V>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, EvaluationModel, Observer, Arg, Call, ConditionalInvocation, Evaluation<V>, Evaluator<V>, Identifiable, Invocation<V>, EvaluationComponent, SupportComponent, Reactive<V>, Request, Scopable, Service, Substitutable

    public class AltInvoker<V>
extends ServiceInvoker<V>
implements ConditionalInvocation
    The alternative Invoker that executes sequentially a collection optional invokers. It invokes the first optInvoker in the collection such that its condition is true.
